@startuml
[*] --> ReceiveVideoSuggestionRequest : The system shall receive a video suggestion request from a user.
ReceiveVideoSuggestionRequest --> IdentifyUser : The system shall identify the user who made the video suggestion request.
IdentifyUser --> GatherVideos : The system shall gather different types of videos simultaneously based on the user's profile or preferences, trending videos from the user’s area, videos with similar tags, videos from similar genres, and promoted videos .
GatherVideos --> AddDetails : The system shall add additional details such as thumbnails and view counts to the suggested videos.
AddDetails --> SendVideos : The system shall send the suggested videos to the user.
@enduml
